t-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">【答案解析】风湿性疾病泛指影响骨、关节及其周围软组织</span>,如肌肉、滑囊、肌腱、筋膜神经等的一组疾病。其病因可以是感染性、免疫性、代谢性、内分泌性、退行性、地理环境性、遗传性肿瘤性等。病情经过往往体现了病理过程:退行性病变呈现缓慢、隐袭的发病经过;创伤则与相关事件有明确的联系;痛风等晶体性关节炎,多起病急骤(24小时内达到高峰),但有自限性,多于1周左右缓解;反应性关节炎常在感染后数周内相继出现皮肤黏膜损害和关节炎;自身免疫性风湿病则多呈静止、活动交替,自发缓解、反复加重的慢性经过。对治疗反应个体差异大。</span></p><p><br/></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6981,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:54:21","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:54:21","isTrue":false,"questionId":2540,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">病程多呈慢性经过</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6982,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:54:21","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:54:21","isTrue":false,"questionId":2540,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">临床表现差异很大</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6983,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:54:21","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:54:21","isTrue":false,"questionId":2540,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">反复发作与缓解交替出现</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6984,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:54:21","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:54:21","isTrue":false,"questionId":2540,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">免疫学异常表现复杂</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6985,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:54:21","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:54:21","isTrue":true,"questionId":2540,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对治疗反应的个体差异不大</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1257,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:20","updateTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:20","name":"风湿A1","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1022,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:21","name":"风湿A1","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2536,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","topicId":null,"tagId":1257,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":5,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">晨僵在哪类关节炎中表现最为突出</span></span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">【答案解析】本题是基础知识考题，考核对</span>RA临床表现的了解。类风湿关节炎常伴有晨僵，指受累关节于静止后特别是清晨出现较长时间(＞1h)的僵硬，如胶粘着样感觉。为本病活动性指标之一。在OA和AS也可有晨僵，但持续时间较短，并不如趾病人常见。感染性和风湿性关节炎病人无明显的晨僵。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6961,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","isTrue":false,"questionId":2536,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">骨性关节炎</span>(OA)&nbsp;</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6962,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","isTrue":true,"questionId":2536,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">类风湿性关节炎（</span>RA)</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6963,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","isTrue":false,"questionId":2536,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">强直性脊柱炎</span>(AS)&nbsp;</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6964,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","isTrue":false,"questionId":2536,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">感染性关节炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6965,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:54","isTrue":false,"questionId":2536,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">风湿性关节炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1257,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:20","updateTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:20","name":"风湿A1","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1022,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:21","name":"风湿A1","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2534,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:40","topicId":null,"tagId":1022,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":4,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">治疗风湿性疾病的药物，下列哪项是错误</span></span></p><p><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">【答案解析】</span>风湿病种类繁多,多为慢性疾病,明确诊断后应尽早开始治疗,治疗的目的是改善预后,保持关节、脏器的功能,缓解相关症状，提高生活质量。治疗措施包括一般治疗(教育 、生活方式、物理治疗、锻炼、对症等)，药物治疗,手术治疗(矫形、滑膜切除、关节置换等)。抗风湿病药物主要包括非甾体抗炎药(NSAIDs)、糖皮质激素、改变病情抗风湿药(DMARDs)及生物制剂。布洛芬——非甾体抗炎药：通过抑制环氧化酶(COX),从而抑制花生四烯酸转化为前列腺素,起到抗炎、解热、镇痛的效果。该药应用广泛,起效快,镇痛效果好，但不能控制原发病的病情进展。 青霉胺C、环磷酰胺——改变病情抗风湿药：该组药物的共同特点是具有改善病情和延缓病情进展的作用，可以防止和延缓特别是类风湿关节炎的关节骨结构破坏。 强的松—— 糖皮质激素：该类药物具有强大的抗炎作用和免疫抑制作用因而被用于治疗风湿性疾病,是治疗多种结缔组织病的一线药物。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6951,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:40","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:40","isTrue":false,"questionId":2534,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">布洛芬</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6952,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:40","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:40","isTrue":false,"questionId":2534,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">青霉胺</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6953,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:40","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:40","isTrue":false,"questionId":2534,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">环磷酰胺</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6954,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:40","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:40","