ly:楷体\">及其周围软组织</span>(如肌肉、肌腱、滑膜</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">、滑囊、韧带和软骨等</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\">)及</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">其他相关组织和器官的慢性</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">疾病。其病因可以是感染性、免疫性、代谢性、内分泌性、退行性、地理环境性、遗传性肿瘤性等。风湿性</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">疾病可以</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">是</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">系统性的，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">也</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">可以是局限性的；可以是器质性的，也可以是功能性的。弥漫性结缔组织</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">病</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">是风湿性疾病的重要组成部分，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">但</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">风湿性疾病不只限于弥漫性结缔组织</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">病。</span></span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6916,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:44:59","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:44:59","isTrue":false,"questionId":2527,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">风湿病就是胶原性疾病</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6917,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:44:59","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:44:59","isTrue":false,"questionId":2527,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">风湿病就是结缔组织</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},